OL,3,CFirst section of refurbished Tyne
OL,4,CBridge revealed
OL,6,FJulia Barthram had a sneak peek behind
OL,7,Fthe scenes of the Tyne Bridge
OL,8,Frestoration.
OL,10,FThe first phase of a multi-million
OL,11,Fpound project to restore the Tyne
OL,12,Fbridge to its former glory has been
OL,13,Frevealed.
OL,15,FThe completed work is part of the #32m
OL,16,Fscheme to revamp, repair and re-paint
OL,17,Fthe iconic structure which began last
OL,18,FSeptember.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/7
