OL,3,CFirst section of refurbished Tyne
OL,4,CBridge revealed
OL,6,FIt is being completed in 20 stages as
OL,7,Fweight restrictions on the Grade II-
OL,8,Flisted structure mean that it cannot
OL,9,Fbe entirely covered by scaffolding at
OL,10,Fonce.
OL,12,FSo far, the work has included
OL,13,Fsteelwork repairs while the parapet
OL,14,Fand underside of the bridge have been
OL,15,Fgiven a fresh coat of the bridge's
OL,16,Fdistinctive green paint.
OL,18,FThe work is due to be finished in
OL,19,FOctober 2028 in time for the bridge's
OL,20,Fcentenary celebration.
