OL,3,CFirst section of refurbished Tyne
OL,4,CBridge revealed
OL,6,FIt is estimated that over the course
OL,7,Fof the four-year project, 1,000
OL,8,Frepairs will need to be carried out.
OL,10,FThese include steelwork repairs, grit
OL,11,Fblasting and re-painting, as well as
OL,12,Fconcrete repairs, drainage
OL,13,Fimprovements, and masonry repairs.
OL,15,FThe bridge deck will also be
OL,16,Fwaterproofed, resurfaced and the
OL,17,Fbridge joints replaced.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/7
