OL,3,CFirst section of refurbished Tyne
OL,4,CBridge revealed
OL,6,FCllr Karen Kilgour, deputy leader of
OL,7,FNewcastle City Council, said: "This is
OL,8,Fa really exciting time for the project
OL,9,Fwith the first coat of green paint
OL,10,Fbeing applied. It truly is a welcome
OL,11,Ftransformation seeing this much-loved
OL,12,Ficon being restored to its former
OL,13,Fglory.
OL,15,F"This has been a real labour of love
OL,16,Ffor all those involved in this major
OL,17,Fscheme and the teams have worked non-
OL,18,Fstop since the project got underway
OL,19,Fthis April.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/7
