OL,3,CFirst section of refurbished Tyne
OL,4,CBridge revealed
OL,6,F"It will be a proud day when the
OL,7,Frestoration is complete and we see the
OL,8,Fbridge shining proudly once again on
OL,9,Fthe Tyneside skyline."
OL,11,FNeil Wilkinson, from Gateshead Council
OL,12,Fadded: "It's fantastic to see this
OL,13,Frich green shaade of paint back on the
OL,14,Fbridge, bringing it to it's best.
OL,16,F"Everyone knows what the Tyne bridge
OL,17,Fmeans to this area, and it's going to
OL,18,Fbe great for people to see the new
OL,19,Fpaint as they travel back and forth,
OL,20,Fto understand what the finished
OL,21,Frestoration will look like."
