OL,3,CFirst section of refurbished Tyne
OL,4,CBridge revealed
OL,6,FAround 70,000 vehicles use the bridge
OL,7,Fto cross the River Tyne every day, and
OL,8,Fsince April two of the four lanes have
OL,9,Fbeen closed.
OL,11,FThese restrictions, which cut the
OL,12,Fcapacity of the bridge in half, are
OL,13,Fexpected to remain in place until 2025.
